title: Install OS X Yosemite .app 10.10.5 from apple + TransMac
description:
This download contains the original and untouched InstallESD.dmg (10.10.5) from apple.

There is also the pretty handy tool "TransMac" with a fixed exe included.
With TransMac you can easy create a bootable usb stick in windows. No need to have a real mac.

Just install the little tool and copy the fixed exe into the programm directory.
Simple as that. 

Enjoy
